<TEXT>
<P>
Dayton Hudson Corp. of Minneapolis announced that Marvin Goldstein has been 
named chairman and chief executive of its Dayton Hudson Department Store Co. 
Goldstein has been president of DHDSC, overseeing all merchandising and stores 
functions. Goldstein, 46, started his retailing career in 1966 as a management 
trainee at Dayton's. 
</P>
