BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $30 Wednesday when Hat Parade ran out of 
the money in the sixth race. Bob, who started the meeting with a mythical 
$1,000 bankroll, is now at $1,113. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is $30 to win on Midday Melody in the first. 
</P>
<P>
Wednesday's Bankroll $1,143 
</P>
<P>
Wednesday's Loss $30 
</P>
<P>
