<P>
JEWISH CONFERENCE SLATED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Tikkun magazine and Hillel, the Jewish student organization at UCLA, are 
sponsoring a conference of liberal and progressive Jewish intellectuals to be 
held at the Westwood campus on Saturday and Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
