<TEXT>
<P>
The UC Irvine Child Development Center is selling raffle and picnic tickets to 
raise money for playground equipment at the school, which serves hyperactive 
children who are in kindergarten through fifth grade. 
</P>
<P>
Raffle prizes include a trip to San Francisco and a color television. The 
picnic, for adults and children, is scheduled for 11 a.m. to 4 p.m. Saturday at 
TeWinkle Park in Costa Mesa. Raffle tickets are $1; the suggested price for 
picnic tickets is $5. 
</P>
<P>
