20 to lead the Vanguards (11-7, 3-1) at El Modena. The Vanguards led, 24-12, at 
the end of the first quarter and were never challenged. Chris Kirby scored 20 
points for Villa Park (1-13, 0-4). 
</P>
<P>
Santa Ana 60, Canyon 55 -- Chauncy Woolridge returned after a two-game absence 
for personal reasons and scored 13 points to lead host Santa Ana (7-10, 2-2). 
Canyon (9-9, 2-2) trailed by 20 points going into the final quarter but cut the 
final deficit to five points with some accurate free-throw shooting and by 
forcing turnovers. 
</P>
