deficit at Cerritos Regional Park. Santa Margarita (6-9, 3-3) pulled to within 
two points, 32-30, at halftime, then outscored Whitney, 17-8, in the third 
quarter. Dan Bathey scored 26 points and Jeff Layne 17 for the Eagles, and each 
had 10 rebounds. 
</P>
