<P>
The death of a fan who clashed with police at the Forum in Inglewood during a 
Grateful Dead concert last December won't change the group's plans to play 
there again in February, a band spokesman said. 
</P>
<P>
The Grateful Dead will perform at the Forum Feb. 9, 10 and 11, spokesman Dennis 
